com.sdklite.aapt

Class ResourceTable.Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sdklite.aapt.ResourceTable.Entry
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResourceTable.MapEntry, ResourceTable.ValueEntry
    Enclosing class:
    ResourceTable

    public abstract static class ResourceTable.Entry
extends Object
    This is the beginning of information about an entry in the resource table. It holds the reference to the name of this entry, and is immediately followed by one of:
    • A ResourceValue structure, if FLAG_COMPLEX is not set.
    • An array of ResourceTable.Map structures, if FLAG_COMPLEX is set.
    These supply a set of name/value mappings of data.
